  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UPDATE: Currently game under slow development due war in Ukraine :( </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Love shark-themed games? Dive in and start hunting!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chase after schools of fish as a hungry ocean predator.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of a powerful shark and explore the depths filled with life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax, swim freely, and enjoy the calm of the underwater world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep your energy up by eating smaller fish—but stay alert, because larger predators may be lurking nearby.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready to begin your adventure? Dive in and start the hunt!</p>",
